com.igeekinc.util

Interface FileLike

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ClientFile

    public interface FileLike
    Interface for things that are similar to, but not quite a java.io.File Used so that we can have RestoreFileDescriptors and ClientFiles be used in FSTraverser even though they are very different beasts
